u8BLrbsbNzE.title: Cumulus Formations
u8BLrbsbNzE.description: Clear skies, soothed darkness, yet a quick shower followed by sun. Appearing clouds, fading clouds, enigmatic as life itself.

J-MDo1PmIC0.title: Ave Astra et Viator
J-MDo1PmIC0.description: The traveler's spirit wanders on, showered in starlight evermore.

3H5HUkW1_xw.title: Lustrous Moonlight
3H5HUkW1_xw.description: Stainless is the clear night. The moon is silver bright. Fill my cup, and make sure it brims up.

fBzgfwmZ5x4.title: Fabulous Foresight
fBzgfwmZ5x4.description: Though everything may change in a flash, my strategies can keep things under control.

J83VAXHJ4GA.title: Upon the Firmament
J83VAXHJ4GA.description: Gaze up, and study the laws of astronomy. Look down, and observe the features of geography. Only then would the formation of night and day be clear in your mind.

fqCfqRwVsLY.title: Exquisite Ingenuity
fqCfqRwVsLY.description: By measuring, the load-bearing of starskiffs derived. By examination, the quality of material determined. Meticulously, detailed blueprints drafted. Meticulously followed, exquisite delves constructed.

DHw5h02QyLI.title: Deerstalker
DHw5h02QyLI.description: A desperate deer will resort to any means to escape.

4mJfZLa49ik.title: Anthropic Domain
4mJfZLa49ik.description: The sun rises and sets, the moon waxes and wanes. The days turn, the seasons pass. The land thrives, the people prosper. As the galaxy stretches overhead.

NugKwBuQLAk.title: Thundering Chariot
NugKwBuQLAk.description: Thunder roars and rumbles, after lightning flashes and tears the skyfall.

dtP08Ly_h5Y.title: Blade Abracadabra
dtP08Ly_h5Y.description: Blade dancing amongst the willow, light streaking out of the sheath.
